Scheduler - Alarms and reminders
================================
Copyright 2016-2019 Juliette Monsel <j_4321@protonmail.com>

Changelog
---------
- Version 1.2.0
    * Add command line argument -U to update highlighted date in the calendar widget
    * Add service file scheduler@.service to update the highlighted date on resume
    * Add a button in Settings to refresh reminders after APScheduler's updates
    * Fix invisible timer widget when changing screen size
    * Fix row colors when filtering events by category
    * Fix crash when changing twice the date of an event
    
- Version 1.1.1
    * Fix widget disappearance in Plasma desktop
    * Improve dates and legend in pomodoro stat graph
    * Fix French translation
    * Fix error when deleting unworked task

- Version 1.1.0
	* Add compatibility with matplotlib<3.0.0
	* Use [tkcalendar](https://github.com/j4321/tkcalendar/) module
	* Use babel to display dates in local format
	* Improve dates displayed in events widget
	* Use mpg123 as sound player
	* Show error if 'Summary' field is empty
	* Fix call to notify.py for Ubuntu

- Version 1.0.0
    * Initial release
